query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(c o) */ select c.c_city,
s.s_city,
d.d_year,
sum(l.l_revenue) AS revenue
from customer AS c
inner join orders AS o
on o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND ( c.c_city = 'UNITED KI1' OR c.c_city = 'UNITED KI5')
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
inner join date AS d
on o.o_orderdate = d.d_datekey AND d.d_yearmonth = 'Dec1997'
inner join supplier AS s
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND ( s.s_city = 'UNITED KI1' OR s.s_city = 'UNITED KI5') group by c.c_city, s.s_city, d.d_year order by d.d_year asc, revenue desc;
